# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# Veliora.AI — Environment Variables Template
# Copy this file to .env and fill in your actual values.
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

# ─── Application ───
APP_NAME=Veliora.AI
APP_VERSION=1.0.0
DEBUG=true
CORS_ORIGINS=http://localhost:3000,http://localhost:5173

# ─── Supabase ───
SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project.supabase.co
SUPABASE_KEY=your-supabase-anon-key
SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=your-supabase-service-role-key
SUPABASE_JWT_SECRET=your-supabase-jwt-secret

# ─── Upstash Redis (REST API) ───
UPSTASH_REDIS_URL=https://your-redis.upstash.io
UPSTASH_REDIS_TOKEN=your-upstash-redis-token

# ─── Gemini API (Free Tier) ───
GEMINI_API_KEY=your-gemini-api-key
GEMINI_MODEL=gemini-1.5-flash
GEMINI_EMBEDDING_MODEL=text-embedding-004
GEMINI_EMBEDDING_DIMENSIONS=768

# ─── Deepgram (Speech-to-Text) ───
DEEPGRAM_API_KEY=your-deepgram-api-key

# ─── Cartesia (Text-to-Speech) ───
CARTESIA_API_KEY=your-cartesia-api-key
CARTESIA_MODEL=sonic-2

# ─── HuggingFace Serverless API ───
HF_API_TOKEN=your-huggingface-api-token
HF_RERANKER_MODEL=cross-encoder/ms-marco-MiniLM-L-6-v2
HF_IMAGE_MODEL=stabilityai/stable-diffusion-xl-base-1.0

# ─── Vector Search ───
VECTOR_TOP_K=50
RERANK_TOP_K=8

# ─── Redis Cache TTLs (seconds) ───
REDIS_CONTEXT_TTL=86400
REDIS_GAME_STATE_TTL=7200
REDIS_CONTEXT_MAX_MESSAGES=50

# ─── Background Workers ───
XP_FLUSH_INTERVAL=60
DIARY_CRON_HOUR=0
